===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|lepen}}, from {{inh|en|ang|hlēapan}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*hlaupan}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*hlaupaną}}. 

Cognate with {{cog|fy|ljeppe||to jump}}, {{cog|nl|lopen||to run; to walk}}, {{cog|de|laufen||to run; to walk}}, {{cog|da|løbe}}, {{cog|nb|løpe}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*klewb-||to spring, stumble}} (compare {{cog|lt|šlùbti}} ‘to become lame’, {{m|lt|klùbti}} ‘to stumble’).

